content.rendered: Baker Manock & Jensen, P.C. is a law firm in Fresno, CA serving businesses and their owners and executives in central California and beyond.  Their expertise in a variety of industries extends across all areas of agriculture, food production, and manufacturing, and they have expertise in a range of disciplines, including water law, tax, and complex business planning.
